file.content:
# Test for an API where we can't generate any examples

openapi: 3.0.1
info:
   title: Regression test for an API which doesn't have any example
   version: 0.0.1
paths:
  /op:
    get:
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: object
              properties:
                propery:
                  type: string
              required:
                - property
      responses:
        '200':
          description: 'OK'
